integrity he said were here for the long pull 
dahl said he tried to look back a few years when so much of the 
nations agriculture was going through the financial wringer and 
what farmer mac might have done to help 
and i think it would have been a lot easier a lot more stable 
if we had had it he said thats what we need to try and do in 
the future 
