worse 
the former president reminisced that in his days as a 
congressman and senator when the cold war began the chief goal of 
the united states was to defeat communism now he said the 
greatest responsibility is to see that freedom works 
the 77yearold nixon has become more visible in recent months 
through his visit to china a dinner with president bush to discuss 
that trip and his effort to help bush convince the senate to 
sustain a veto 
nixons briefings were one more step in his increasing political 
acceptance 
