fruitful and lively he said the visit opened a formal series of 
consultations within nato on german unification and related 
security issues it will be synchronized with talks between the two 
germanys and the four victorious world war ii powers britain 
france the united states and the soviet union 
kohl met first with woerner and then with the ambassadors of the 
16 alliance nations 
