mantailored outfits to satisfy the woman that identifies his 
style with the transposition of menswear into womens clothing 
the new armani pant suit in ultra light wool tweeds inspired by 
silk tie patterns has a longer jacket with narrower shoulders but 
a wider rounded base the trousers are baggy and cuffed a 
masculine shirt with mandarine collar completes the outfit 
