<TEXT>
two weeks before her fraud and racketeering 
trial imelda marcos is trying to follow her lawyers advice but 
sometimes its hard for a woman used to the world as her forum to 
keep quiet 
for months the 60yearold mrs marcos has ignored incessant 
interview requests choosing instead to pore over legal documents 
in a cool dark room that was once the wine cellar of her makiki 
heights home 
her new lead attorney wyoming maverick gerry spence said the 
only way the usually outspoken mrs marcos will get a fair trial in 
this country is if she keeps her mouth shut and lets the evidence 
