thrift office from seizing olympic for 10 days unless the agency 
provides the court and the sampl with six hours notice he scheduled 
a hearing for tuesday 
the case has wide ramifications over the past year the 
government has seized more than 380 sampls in nearly 40 states and 
has closed or sold 50 of those 
