confirmed that the appointments would cost 5 million but said the 
measures he had introduced the past two years ago had saved three 
times that amount 
in an interview at the thai beach resort of jomtien where he is 
attending an international conference on education mayor called 
british media criticism of his moves misleading and 
illinformed 
