600000 sailors and 200000 marines 
untermeyer who said he longs to leave personnel work and 
return to a policy rule has stayed off the social circuit 
partly to avoid being buttonholed by job seekers 
he routinely logs 12 to 14hour days customarily getting by on 
four or five hours of sleep a night 
at his desk on a recent sunday afternoon untermeyer 
acknowledged that 1989 had its grim points but it had its 
upside too i also met the woman that im now engaged to marry 
he and diana c kendrick 27 executive assistant to c boyden 
gray the white house counsel plan an october wedding 
it was a white house romance you might say that we met on a 
sunday working on paperwork which is exactly whats happening 
now 
