a republican congressman from upstate new york 
once was nominated for vice president on the grounds that he used 
to drive president lyndon b johnson nuts by that kind of test 
rep richard a gephardt may yet wind up on a democratic ticket 
the house majority leader seems to be the democrat most likely 
