was among the scientists and volunteers who spent four days 
unearthing the remains of a prehistoric mammoth 
but it was a very exciting find he said 
the nearly complete skeleton buried 10 feet deep was 
discovered by a bulldozer operator preparing the way for a resort 
along the ohio river 
