bank holding company based in columbus ga to issue the credit 
cards synovus said 
total system services inc a columbusbased credit card service 
company controlled by synovus would process the transactions from 
the atampt cards under the plan tss said tss is the nations 
secondlargest credit card transaction processing company 
atampt spokesman bruce reid on wednesday confirmed the 
negotiations 
were in a highly competitive marketplace and looking at a 
number of ways of enhancing the atampt credit card he said the 
card competes with similar cards issued by sprint and mci 
communications corp the secondlargest longdistance phone 
company 
