dissuaded atampt from such a plan said robert morris iii of goldman 
sachs amp co 
sears roebuck and cos discover card was the last separate 
national card to break into the industry and the retailer endured 
several years of steep losses before turning the operation around 
american express began offering its optima revolving charge card 
to holders of its regular credit cards several years ago 
morris said atampt evidently believes it can increase the use of 
its phone network through the new credit cards in addition the 
company would get a share of the interest and fees charged to 
cardholders 
