failure to pay the interest due wednesday under special 
arrangements made last week postponing earlier payment deadlines 
meant campeau went into default on loans from olympia amp york 
developments ltd and edward j debartolo corp 
but the lenders have agreed they will not move to collect their 
collateral without notifying campeau nine days in advance 
the loans total 705 million two loans of 75 million and 150 
